      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "Ford's GT supercar is an incredible, state-of-the-art machine. Regardless, even after it was released, Ford engineers looked for ways to "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "squeeze even more performance"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          " out of the already potent GT."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "After some hard-fought race success, Ford released the GT Competition Series to commemorate their victories. These cars featured "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "several weight-saving measures"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          ", employing materials such as carbon fiber and titanium. Thinner glass was always used."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      10,
      1
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "Major weight savings, though, came from removing the Ford GT's "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "creature comforts"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          ", such as the air conditioning, stereo system, and even the cupholders. For some, this was a bridge too far."
        ]
      ]
    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "As a compromise, Ford built "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "a limited number of Lightweight models"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          ", which included all of the weight saving measures but retained the infotainment system and air conditioning of the standard car."
